1. Michigan submits cryptocurrency reserve bill to allow state government to invest in crypto assets;
2. zkLend: Hackers did not respond before the deadline, and will announce fund recovery and release plan next week;
3. Yesterday, the US Bitcoin spot ETF had a net outflow of US$156.78 million, with net outflow for 4 consecutive days;
4. Yesterday, the US Ethereum spot ETF had a net inflow of US$12.83 million;
5. The President of El Salvador met with Michael Saylor to discuss Bitcoin-related issues;
6. A whale spent US$2.54 million to buy 2 memecoins named after CZ's dog;
7. BscScan: Unplanned maintenance is underway, and the current block data is not the latest data;
8. VanEck Consultant: Tether currently holds approximately US$5.3 billion in precious metals and US$7.8 billion in Bitcoin.
